04214 
04215   // Lookup a function pointer from the table,
04216   // or deeper in the stack as necessary.
04217 
04218   template<typename T, typename F>
04219   F call(T &table, F *func)
04220   {
04221     RegalAssert(func);
04222     if (table._enabled && *func)
04223       return *func;
04224 
04225     T *i = &table;
04226     RegalAssert(i);
04227 
04228     RegalAssert(reinterpret_cast<void *>(func)>=reinterpret_cast<void *>(i));
04229     RegalAssert(reinterpret_cast<void *>(func)< reinterpret_cast<void *>(i+1));
04230 
04231     const std::size_t offset = reinterpret_cast<char *>(func) - reinterpret_cast<char *>(i);
04232 
04233     F f = *func;
04234 
04235     // Step down the stack for the first available function in an enabled table
04236 
04237     while (!f || !i->_enabled)
04238     {
04239       // Find the next enabled dispatch table
04240       for (i = i->next(); !i->_enabled; i = i->next()) { RegalAssert(i); }
04241 
04242       // Get the function pointer; extra cast through void* is to avoid -Wcast-align spew
04243       RegalAssert(i);
04244       RegalAssert(i->_enabled);
04245       f = *reinterpret_cast<F *>(reinterpret_cast<void *>(reinterpret_cast<char *>(i)+offset));
04246     }
04247 
04248     return f;
04249   }
04250 
04251 }
04252 
04253 struct DispatchTable
04254 {
04255   bool           _enabled;
04256   DispatchTable *_prev;
04257   DispatchTable *_next;
04258 };
04259 
04260 struct DispatchTableGL : public DispatchTable, Dispatch::GL
04261 {
04262   template<typename T> T call(T *func) { return Dispatch::call(*this,func);                                }
04263   inline DispatchTableGL *next()       { return reinterpret_cast<DispatchTableGL *>(DispatchTable::_next); }
04264 };
04265 
04266 struct DispatchTableGlobal : public DispatchTable, Dispatch::Global
04267 {
04268   DispatchTableGlobal();
04269   ~DispatchTableGlobal();
04270 
04271   template<typename T> T call(T *func) { return Dispatch::call(*this,func);                                    }
04272   inline DispatchTableGlobal *next()   { return reinterpret_cast<DispatchTableGlobal *>(DispatchTable::_next); }
04273 };
04274 
04275 extern DispatchTableGlobal dispatchTableGlobal;
